title: Next pilot in the autumn
content: The enrolment for the spring pilot has ended, so it's no longer possible to sign up. We'll have another pilot coming up next autumn - stay tuned for that. The deadline for finishing this spring's pilot is the end of May.
author: The UniTandem team

title: Enrolment on autumn's pilot
content: The enrolment for the autumn pilot will be open 17.8.2020 - 13.9.2020 here: https://www.lyyti.in/unitandemS20. Before enrolling, make sure you've found a Tandem partner on this website.
author: The UniTandem team

title: No support in the summer
content: The UniTandem team is out of office 6.6. - 2.8.2020 and there's no support available.
author: The UniTandem team
